<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Sterge Cont</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body style="background-color: <%= theme === 'dark' ? '#222' : '#f0f4f8' %>; color: <%= theme === 'dark' ? '#fff' : '#333' %>; font-family: Arial; padding: 50px; text-align: center;">
    
    <div class="card" style="max-width: 400px; margin: auto; padding: 30px; border: 2px solid #e74c3c; <%= theme === 'dark' ? 'background: #333; color: white;' : '' %>">
        <h2 style="color: #e74c3c; margin-top: 0;">⚠️ Atentie!</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.5;">Esti pe cale sa iti stergi contul definitiv.<br>Aceasta actiune <strong>nu poate fi anulata</strong>.</p>
        
        <form action="/sterge-cont" method="POST" style="margin-top: 25px;">
            <button type="submit" style="background-color: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 12px 20px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; width: 100%;">Da, sterge contul meu</button>
        </form>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <a href="/profil" style="color: #0077b6; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">Nu, du-ma inapoi</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>